title: Protect the bearer
lyrics: [] of divine form, send away the discordant clatter of raging plague, air-borne, infiltrating pain, heavy-spiriting, flesh-wasting, melting, from the hollows of the veins.
Great Iao, great Sabaoth, protect the bearer. Phoebus of the unshorn hair, archer, drive away the cloud of plague. Iao, God Abrasax, bring help.
